data.description: This charming 4 bed, 2 bath split level home is located in a quiet neighborhood, minutes away from Lakewood Beach Park. The property has been well cared for with many updates and upgrades over the years. Enter directly into the open concept main living space and preview this home’s many updates. The living room has exposed wood beams, neutral walls, and LVP flooring that runs throughout the home. The remodeled eat-in kitchen features barstool seating, stainless steel appliances, a window looking out to the backyard, and white marble style backsplash. Both bathrooms have been updated with modern vanities and new showers/tubs. The 4 bedrooms are all carpeted with their own closets. Each set of bedrooms has their own bathroom. The fully fenced in backyard has mature trees, and a shed ideal for storing outdoor tools. Don't miss out, schedule your appointment today!
